{"tid":1715911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽]由721開始香港已是軍政府狀態, 所以","createTime":"2019-11-13T08:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T14:17:57.000Z","uid":47659,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"56f82de31f75d605454e6f86f217fabf6382fcae","tid":1715911,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:02:57.000Z","msg":"唔好諗得港共政府有幾高張<br />\n政治問題, 政治解決, 原本道理的確如此<br />\n但經過過去5個月警慌犯下多種人道同國際戰犯級罪行後<br />\n政府根本已經驚呢3萬個object仲多過驚示威, 直頭係驚佢地多過驚中央<br />\n<br />\n所以大家可唔可以改變下成個思維?<br />\n唔好晒時間猜忌政府行緊咩棋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再妄圖體制內抗爭 (立法會區議會司法覆核監警會等等) 可以對抗警暴, <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就算五大訴求 如此卑微既政治訴求 都早就顯得同今日既戰爭局面格格不入</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地既首要敵人係呢3萬個Object</span>, 當然<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有需要時我地要預備連同埋政權連根拔起</span><br />\n唔好再比淋病港共spin去&quot;用暴力換取政治訴求&quot;呢個偽命題<br />\n<br />\n我地而家唔係為政治訴求而戰, 係為 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保家衛國 </strong></span></span>而戰 <br />\n<br />\n天佑我城,天佑中大!<br />\n光復香港 時代革命!!!"},{"pid":"968785bf0435544bf0ab44671e8ae1730897832e","tid":1715911,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:04:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea39f7ecd36a5c0d1e878bfd258656341d28ed1b","tid":1715911,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:04:58.000Z","msg":"推、"},{"pid":"e9475d23e429e78b8c35e057125959bce1ec9847","tid":1715911,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:10:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a48ae0fbe3179f124a83bdb099b0a5a472a6153d","tid":1715911,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2ef964e09f3241e3725f3211c6fee18272208a","tid":1715911,"uid":263577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:13:10.000Z","msg":"保家衛國，